{"tid":1043376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Fb入稟法院　控中國4公司和3人售假帳戶","createTime":"2019-03-02T08:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T12:31:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cebcc3ac72a962fdb2e409a07b757883df635c6d","tid":1043376,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190302/mobile/bkn-20190302131812136-0302_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190302%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190302131812136-0302_00972_001.html&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=6876bafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190302/mobile/bkn-20190302131812136-0302_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國社交網站Facebook（Fb）及旗下的應用程式Instagram（IG），周五（3月1日）入稟美國三藩市聯邦法院，控告4間中國公司以及3名人士，於過去2年販賣假帳戶、讚好次數和追隨者人數。涉事公司暫未回應。 <br />\n<br />\n起訴書指，有中國公司製造假帳戶，並於6個網站列登廣告。涉事公司名稱為「9 Xiu Shenzhen」、「9 Xiu Feishu」、「9 Xiufei」、「Home Network」，它們全數在中國深圳和福建龍巖設立，是電子和硬件製造商的附屬公司，同時提供軟件和網絡廣告服務。 <br />\n<br />\nFb及IG在起訴書提及，虛假帳戶可用於發送垃圾郵件和網絡釣魚活動、虛假資訊活動、營銷騙局、欺詐廣告，以及其他詐騙計劃。起訴書又指，除了Fb和IG外，購物網站亞馬遜、美國蘋果公司、領英（LinkedIn）、Twitter等亦受影響。"},{"pid":"488b34eb55e78a50ff97d6edda051148edbe8b50","tid":1043376,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開牌原來係國企黎<br />\n<br />\n口交部：強烈譴責別國干涉國家內政"},{"pid":"41645a73e692a30db8c42161b418198d110386c8","tid":1043376,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb3a8182a1a0f8ac76fc64aa84fdc2d50d7d1fa","tid":1043376,"uid":54930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.iniiter.com//img/2015/11/4353fdc15836c05704a339cb7891f747f3c3360af24c7a2409